Class IphcAddress

  • java.lang.Object
    • inet.ipaddr.IPAddressString
      • de.htw.ai.loz.gpan.lpan.header.IphcAddress
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    inet.ipaddr.HostIdentifierString, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<inet.ipaddr.IPAddressString>
    public class IphcAddress
extends inet.ipaddr.IPAddressString
    Wraps an IPv6 address and provides methods to check it for compatibility ( @link https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6282 ).
